.modal(
  role="dialog"
  aria-labelledby="modalTitle"
  aria-describedby="modalDescription"
)
  //- https://habr.com/ru/post/350232/ прочитать подробнее
  .modal__content
    header.modal__heading
      slot(name="heading")
        | {{title}}
      button.modal__close(
        type="button"
        aria-label="Close modal"
        @click="closeModal"
      )
        | ×
    div.modal__body
      slot(name="body")
        | Body text
    footer.modal__actions
      slot(name="footer")
        button.modal__button(
          type="button"
          aria-label="Close modal"
          @click="closeModal"
        )
          | OK
